{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy is a challenging 2D platformer offering 22 interesting and challenging levels filled with many traps. Complete them as quickly as possible and beat your previous time records!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u258e<strong>The goal of the game is to overcome obstacles in a short time.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your skills in Easy mode to complete even difficult levels quickly. Compete with other players on your high scores in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/extras/1__v2__online-video-cutter.com___1___5_.gif?t=1739388384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u258e<strong>Challenge \u2014 The &quot;Hard&quot; Level</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The &quot;Hard&quot; level offers you maximum difficulty. It's not just hard \u2014 it's a challenge that no one has passed yet \u2014 be the first! Be sure to turn on the camera after completing this level, the developer has prepared a gift for you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Information about the &quot;Hard&quot; level: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The level does not relate to the plot, so it is unlocked immediately along with the first level. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> More than 70 obstacles </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The average score of the complete passage is 6% </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Time to complete is 30 minutes (after which you will return to the beginning of the level)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u258e Study \u2014 your skills</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If the level turned out to be too easy for you, please note: each level requires new tactics and time to study it. Test which strategies help you overcome the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/extras/_4__online-video-cutter.com_.gif?t=1739388384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u258e Survival \u2014 don 't relax</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be prepared for the unexpected \u2014 in Easy, any step can be decisive. Estimate the number of obstacles and your chances of passing through them to keep your completed scores. Will you be able to complete this challenging platformer?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/extras/0114_3___online-video-cutter.com_.gif?t=1739388384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u258e\u00a0Records</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a timer in each level, and your best time gets into the high score section. You can share your records on social media with the tag &quot;#XG_Easy&quot;. This way, the developers are more likely to notice you and give you a gift for a decent result or an epic passage. Upgrade your skills!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739388384","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/page.bg.jpg?t=1739388384","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/879a7800bfdc5907ba2e64a9c319cc583e8dd889/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739388384","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252530/879a7800bfdc5907ba2e64a9c319cc583e8dd889/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739388384","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy is a challenging 2D platformer offering 22 interesting and c